channel.title: Error importing Whonix 14 images (Debian Jessie)
channel.description:
Trying to use the command from the install instructions:
[code]virsh -c qemu:///system define Whonix-Gateway*.xml[/code]
I get this error:
[code] error: Failed to define domain from Whonix-Gateway-14.0.0.7.4.xml error: unsupported configuration: unexpected feature 'pmu'[/code]
Any suggestions?
